data.description: NEW YEAR, NEW PRICE!! Nestled in the heart of Ormond Beach, this pristine and furnished, 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom, Florida room, enclosed porch, paver patio, 1800+ square foot townhome is a true gem, offering an array of features that enhance the coastal living experience. As you approach, a charming front paver courtyard welcomes you, setting the stage for the warm and inviting atmosphere that awaits within. Inside, the eat-in kitchen boasts a bay window and skylight flooding the space with natural light and providing a perfect spot for enjoying morning coffee. The kitchen also offers a convenient built-in desk space, combining functionality with style. The great room/dining room combination is adorned with vaulted ceilings, creating an open and airy ambiance that complements the coastal lifestyle. It's an ideal space for gatherings and relaxation. The oversized owners' retreat provides a private sanctuary, complete with ample space for a cozy reading nook or a personal yoga corner. A standout feature of this home is the Florida room, a versatile space that can be used for entertaining, a home office, or simply as a serene spot to enjoy the beauty of the outdoors. Here, you'll find a wet bar, adding an extra touch of convenience and entertainment. Adjacent, a screened-in porch allows for al fresco dining and relaxation, all while enjoying the comfort of a bug-free environment. Beyond the comforts of this lovely townhome, the community offers amenities for active and social living. Take a dip in the sparkling pool or challenge a friend to a game of tennis. Lawn care is included in the HOA fee, allowing you to relish in a beautifully maintained exterior without the hassle. Conveniently located, this home provides easy access to everything Ormond Beach has to offer, from the pristine beaches to an array of dining and shopping options. Plus, with close proximity to I95, exploring the wider area is a breeze.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Ormond Beach residence your very own. Schedule a showing today for a private tour and start living the coastal dream!
